@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_egstik(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.01)))
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.06 + v0 + 0.52) / 0.06) + wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.28)))
    tmp = 0.36
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.17 - v0 + 0.14) - (v0 + 0.14 + v1 + 0.15)) * wp.abs((v2 + 0.74 + tmp + 0.66)))
    v0 = 0.02
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.33)) / v2)
    v2 = (0.97 * wp.abs(tmp))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
